http.html:
Donna A Walsh REALTOR®

Lake & Company Real Estate

  • Home
  • About
  • Property Search
  • My Listings
  • Lake Real Estate
  • Condos & Co-ops
  • Seattle Info
  • Contact

Welcome to my Website

Donna A Walsh
REALTOR®
206.650.4851

Are you looking for a home in the Seattle area? Wondering what your current home is worth? Would you like help with the sometimes confusing process of buying or selling a home? I can help.

You may use our Property Search page to familiarize yourself with the Seattle real estate market. Once you're on that page, you can refine your home search using our easy-to-navigate menu. If you have any questions, would like more information, or would like to talk to me about selling or buying a home, please contact me.

Over the years I've listed and sold many units in condominium and cooperative projects. Owning an individual unit in a condo or co-op building presents a different set of issues than owning a single-family home, and I can help you understand what to expect.

If you're new to Seattle, look on my Seattle page to get more information about our area. And, if you have any questions or would like more information, I'm here to help.

Lake & Company Real Estate
7801 Green Lake Drive North
Seattle, WA 98103

Donna A Walsh, REALTOR®
